WEBVTT

00:01:19.199 --> 00:01:20.000
For a woman,

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.560
your strikes are far too ruthless, young lady.

00:01:21.599 --> 00:01:22.560
For a man,

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:24.160
your behavior is far too rude, My Lord.

00:01:25.199 --> 00:01:26.600
We agreed we were in the same boat.

00:01:26.600 --> 00:01:28.000
Turning your back on me so soon?

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:31.199
Didn't you say before, My Lord,

00:01:31.199 --> 00:01:31.960
that I wasn't qualified

00:01:31.960 --> 00:01:33.480
to be tied to the same rope as you?

00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:34.960
Yet now you come looking for me.

00:01:35.239 --> 00:01:36.320
It seems you need a favor from me.

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:38.079
Smart people in this palace

00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:39.879
don't necessarily live very long.

00:01:46.399 --> 00:01:47.280
I came to find you

00:01:47.359 --> 00:01:48.560
to make a deal.

00:01:48.719 --> 00:01:49.920
I need to investigate something.

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:52.600
It's more convenient for you to act in the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

00:01:53.079 --> 00:01:54.880
The Bureau of Imperial Attire's warehouse records have errors.

00:01:55.479 --> 00:01:56.880
Secretly find someone to ask around

00:01:57.640 --> 00:01:59.640
about who collected Frost silk last month.

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:02.240
Why hasn't he returned to the army yet?

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:03.799
And he wants to investigate the Frost silk.

00:02:05.320 --> 00:02:06.479
Since it is a partnership,

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:09.240
My Lord, you also need to show some sincerity.

00:02:09.399 --> 00:02:10.359
What do you want?

00:02:10.479 --> 00:02:11.840
The Scar-Soothing Balm from the Imperial Medical Bureau.

00:02:12.679 --> 00:02:13.840
You certainly know what to pick.

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:15.879
I hold the secret formula for it.

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:16.920
I can agree to it.

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:18.680
Thank you for your trust, Lord Gu.

00:02:18.680 --> 00:02:19.599
A pleasure doing business.

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:21.319
How do you know my surname is Gu?

00:02:21.719 --> 00:02:22.599
You investigated me.

00:02:23.959 --> 00:02:25.959
If I didn't even know the background of my partner,

00:02:25.959 --> 00:02:28.159
wouldn't I be handing over my life on a platter?

00:02:28.159 --> 00:02:29.560
This is both caution for myself

00:02:29.560 --> 00:02:30.920
and respect for you, My Lord.

00:02:32.120 --> 00:02:34.439
To find out who I am in just a few days,

00:02:34.599 --> 00:02:35.519
that is not simple.

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:42.560
I didn't expect that seeing Ah Xuan again

00:02:42.719 --> 00:02:43.840
would be under such circumstances.

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:46.000
But why does he, at this very moment,

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:47.040
come to cause trouble for me?

00:02:48.719 --> 00:02:50.040
Her behavior and mannerisms

00:02:50.159 --> 00:02:51.840
are completely unlike an ordinary palace maid.

00:02:52.280 --> 00:02:53.519
What exactly is her background?

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:03.239
Consort Su.

00:03:03.719 --> 00:03:04.840
Entered the palace three years ago.

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:06.000
Has received little imperial favor.

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:07.519
Impatient and jealous.

00:03:07.519 --> 00:03:08.640
Lacks shrewdness.

00:03:09.159 --> 00:03:10.359
Because of her merchant background,

00:03:10.359 --> 00:03:11.359
she is looked down upon.

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:18.080
We have arrived at Yongfu Palace.

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:25.560
The harem is as deep as the sea.

00:03:25.919 --> 00:03:27.400
The concubines have different intentions.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:29.159
The fire in the mourning hall,

00:03:29.759 --> 00:03:31.280
I will start the investigation with you.

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:42.080
Look at this.

00:03:42.520 --> 00:03:43.439
This lotus-patterned gold hairpin,

00:03:43.439 --> 00:03:45.199
is it bright enough against my temples?

00:03:45.479 --> 00:03:47.280
Will His Majesty like it when he sees it?

00:03:47.439 --> 00:03:49.159
Your Highness is born with the beauty of a celestial being.

00:03:49.159 --> 00:03:51.479
Only this hairpin made of nine-layered gold wire

00:03:51.479 --> 00:03:52.560
is worthy of you.

00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:54.199
You have a way with words.

00:03:54.319 --> 00:03:56.520
Of all the gold and silver workshops in the capital,

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:58.319
only my Su family's goldsmiths

00:03:58.319 --> 00:04:00.560
can craft such an exquisite gold hairpin.

00:04:02.439 --> 00:04:03.439
Greetings, Consort Su.

00:04:03.719 --> 00:04:05.479
The maid sent from the Bureau of Imperial Attire is here.

00:04:11.719 --> 00:04:12.719
This slave is Feng Qing.

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:14.840
Wishing Your Highness eternal peace and happiness.

00:04:15.199 --> 00:04:16.439
I heard from Directress Li

00:04:16.439 --> 00:04:17.639
that you are a clever one.

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:19.840
I like useful people the most.

00:04:20.280 --> 00:04:21.840
If you serve me diligently,

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:23.520
I will certainly not treat you unfairly.

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:24.800
Yes.

00:04:33.280 --> 00:04:34.919
Born with such a seductive fox-like look.

00:04:35.159 --> 00:04:36.520
Are you here to serve your master,

00:04:36.520 --> 00:04:37.879
or to seduce His Majesty?

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:39.800
Drag this vixen out for me!

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:41.039
Beaten to death!

00:04:47.520 --> 00:04:49.240
You dare fight back in Yongfu Palace?

00:04:49.240 --> 00:04:50.639
This slave is but a lowly person.

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:53.199
My death would only quell Your Highness's anger for a moment.

00:04:53.560 --> 00:04:54.639
But if this slave lives,

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.360
I will use all my skills

00:04:56.520 --> 00:04:58.560
to win glory for Your Highness before His Majesty.

00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:00.800
If Your Highness does not wish to see this face,

00:05:01.800 --> 00:05:03.000
this slave will simply ruin it.

00:05:44.759 --> 00:05:46.240
This face now

00:05:46.639 --> 00:05:48.120
looks much more pleasing to the eye.

00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:50.920
Directress Li has a good eye for picking people.

00:05:51.079 --> 00:05:52.480
You are a sensible one.

00:05:52.680 --> 00:05:53.879
From now on, along with Bi Hen,

00:05:53.879 --> 00:05:55.160
stay and serve inside the hall.

00:05:55.759 --> 00:05:57.120
As long as you please me,

00:05:57.519 --> 00:05:58.759
gold, silver, pearls, and jade...

00:05:58.759 --> 00:06:00.079
I have plenty of them.

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:01.680
Naturally, I won't treat you poorly.

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:03.639
Here is your reward.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.040
Thank you, Your Highness.

00:06:18.199 --> 00:06:19.720
The Empress Dowager's posthumous birthday is approaching.

00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:21.560
You used to serve in the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

00:06:21.879 --> 00:06:24.120
So put more effort into the making of the clothes.

00:06:24.360 --> 00:06:26.360
I must outshine everyone this time.

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:27.519
Your Highness,

00:06:27.680 --> 00:06:29.839
preparing the palace attire has always been my duty.

00:06:29.879 --> 00:06:31.079
She is just a newcomer;

00:06:31.279 --> 00:06:32.680
I fear she might ruin important matters.

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:34.680
Isn't it good to give you a new helper?

00:06:35.279 --> 00:06:36.079
Rest assured.

00:06:36.240 --> 00:06:37.480
As long as it is done well,

00:06:37.519 --> 00:06:39.160
both of you will be rewarded.

00:06:39.720 --> 00:06:41.079
But if it is not done well,

00:06:41.519 --> 00:06:43.560
you will get another scar on your face.

00:06:45.040 --> 00:06:45.839
Rise.

00:06:54.519 --> 00:06:55.319
Yes.

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:57.079
For the Empress Dowager's posthumous birthday,

00:06:57.279 --> 00:06:58.800
the palace attire must be vibrant.

00:06:58.800 --> 00:07:00.399
Even if I cannot win His Majesty's favor,

00:07:00.680 --> 00:07:02.879
at least I can curry favor with Noble Consort Meng.

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:04.199
As for my preferences,

00:07:04.399 --> 00:07:05.560
you give her some pointers.

00:07:07.759 --> 00:07:08.720
- I obey. - Yes.

00:07:17.759 --> 00:07:18.560
Feng Qing

00:07:19.319 --> 00:07:21.160
The water temperature for the morning wash is crucial.

00:07:21.279 --> 00:07:22.519
It must not be too cold,

00:07:22.519 --> 00:07:23.800
nor can it scald the Mistress.

00:07:23.920 --> 00:07:25.079
You must be extremely careful.

00:07:25.920 --> 00:07:27.439
Thank you for the advice.

00:07:30.839 --> 00:07:31.600
You lowly maid!

00:07:31.839 --> 00:07:32.720
Are you blind?

00:07:33.959 --> 00:07:35.000
And you!

00:07:39.519 --> 00:07:40.160
You...

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:41.560
It was just a basin of spilled water.

00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:43.040
Just go fetch another.

00:07:43.519 --> 00:07:44.519
Sister Bi Hen,

00:07:44.680 --> 00:07:46.240
why be so aggressive?

00:07:46.279 --> 00:07:48.160
Stop putting on an act.

00:07:48.399 --> 00:07:49.920
To stay in Yongfu Palace,

00:07:50.040 --> 00:07:51.680
you'd even harm yourself.

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:52.680
Speak!

00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:54.399
What are you really plotting?

00:07:57.639 --> 00:07:59.439
Serving Her Highness in Yongfu Palace

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:02.199
is better than the drudgery at the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

00:08:02.920 --> 00:08:03.920
Everyone knows

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:05.680
Her Highness is most compassionate to her servants.

00:08:06.079 --> 00:08:07.279
When she bestows rewards,

00:08:07.279 --> 00:08:08.279
she is incredibly generous.

00:08:09.319 --> 00:08:10.399
This gold hairpin,

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:12.759
she gave it just like that.

00:08:13.399 --> 00:08:15.920
You think a broken hairpin is worth showing off?

00:08:16.399 --> 00:08:18.120
I have served Her Highness since childhood.

00:08:18.199 --> 00:08:19.360
Who do you think you are?

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:25.800
We are both servants of Consort Su.

00:08:26.040 --> 00:08:28.120
Instead of waging a war of words here,

00:08:28.319 --> 00:08:29.680
you would be better off focusing

00:08:29.680 --> 00:08:31.399
on selecting fabrics and tailoring clothes.

00:08:31.399 --> 00:08:32.759
To gain the Mistress's appreciation,

00:08:33.040 --> 00:08:35.519
one must rely on true skill.

00:08:36.560 --> 00:08:38.279
It's not for a Witch like you to lecture me.

00:08:38.279 --> 00:08:39.839
Have you forgotten, Sister Bi Hen?

00:08:40.079 --> 00:08:41.519
I come from the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

00:08:41.639 --> 00:08:43.279
I know fabrics best.

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:46.680
Witch, don't be so arrogant here.

00:08:47.040 --> 00:08:48.040
Just you wait.

00:08:56.720 --> 00:08:58.120
Please fetch another basin, sister.

00:08:58.560 --> 00:08:59.319
Thank you.

00:08:59.639 --> 00:09:01.240
You shouldn't make an enemy of Bi Hen.

00:09:01.680 --> 00:09:03.160
Anyone she dislikes

00:09:03.439 --> 00:09:04.639
ends up in a bad state.

00:09:06.759 --> 00:09:09.560
Then do you know that in Yongfu Palace,

00:09:09.959 --> 00:09:11.399
there was a maid named Wen Tang?

00:09:12.079 --> 00:09:13.000
I don't know anything.

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:14.319
And don't mention that person again.

00:09:16.800 --> 00:09:17.839
Wen Xin once said

00:09:18.319 --> 00:09:19.160
her sister Wen Tang

00:09:19.160 --> 00:09:20.879
died of illness in Yongfu Palace.

00:09:21.079 --> 00:09:22.839
But why was that maid so panicked?

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:26.279
Feng Qing.

00:09:27.160 --> 00:09:27.920
Your face...

00:09:28.680 --> 00:09:29.959
Did Consort Su hurt you?

00:09:30.920 --> 00:09:32.879
I should have stopped you from going to Yongfu Palace.

00:09:32.920 --> 00:09:34.560
You hurt yourself trying to help me.

00:09:34.680 --> 00:09:35.560
Don't worry.

00:09:35.800 --> 00:09:37.439
I inflicted the wound on my face myself.

00:09:37.439 --> 00:09:38.560
Just to ensure safety.

00:09:39.759 --> 00:09:41.560
As for your sister Wen Tang,

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.840
give me a little more time.

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:45.279
I will get to the bottom of it.

00:09:45.759 --> 00:09:47.320
But you must be extremely careful too.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:53.879
The Frost silk I asked you to check on,

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:54.960
any leads?

00:09:54.960 --> 00:09:56.120
I asked around and found out.

00:09:56.360 --> 00:09:57.120
Last month,

00:09:57.120 --> 00:09:58.559
Concubine Cao and Consort Su

00:09:58.679 --> 00:10:00.399
both sent people to collect Frost silk.

00:10:01.480 --> 00:10:03.600
Concubine Cao, Consort Su...

00:10:04.799 --> 00:10:06.879
Then the records at the Bureau of Imperial Attire...

00:10:06.879 --> 00:10:08.080
why are they missing?

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:09.440
That, I don't know.

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:12.159
I went to check the ledger first,

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:14.679
but last month's records were torn out.

00:10:14.679 --> 00:10:15.759
Torn out by someone?

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:18.759
By the way,

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:21.639
I need your help with one more thing.

00:11:25.559 --> 00:11:27.240
The palace dress for Her Highness is embroidered.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:28.039
Tomorrow at the Hour of the Sheep,

00:11:28.039 --> 00:11:30.559
will you come with me to present it to Her Highness?

00:11:30.559 --> 00:11:31.879
All right, we'll go together.

00:11:39.399 --> 00:11:41.039
Sister Bi Hen, why are you snatching my things?

00:11:41.159 --> 00:11:42.000
Insolence!

00:11:42.159 --> 00:11:43.960
Everything in the palace belongs to our masters.

00:11:44.080 --> 00:11:45.120
How can anything be yours?

00:11:45.120 --> 00:11:46.639
I just finished embroidering this dress for Her Highness.

00:11:46.639 --> 00:11:48.159
What gives you the right to snatch it by force?

00:11:48.480 --> 00:11:49.519
You lowly wretch.

00:11:49.759 --> 00:11:51.200
You dare act wild with me?

00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:53.480
This was clearly a task assigned to me by Her Highness.

00:11:53.480 --> 00:11:55.440
I spent days and nights embroidering it.

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:57.159
I wanted to present it to Her Highness myself.

00:11:57.159 --> 00:11:59.279
This is new fabric from the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

00:11:59.279 --> 00:12:00.840
A rare shade of tender-leaf yellow.

00:12:00.840 --> 00:12:02.840
I asked someone early on to save it for Her Highness.

00:12:03.159 --> 00:12:05.159
You merely embroidered a few patterns.

00:12:05.360 --> 00:12:06.440
And you want to steal the credit?

00:12:10.120 --> 00:12:10.919
Just as expected.

00:12:11.159 --> 00:12:12.120
The fish has taken the bait.

00:12:13.279 --> 00:12:14.279
Are you all right?

00:12:22.039 --> 00:12:24.559
This dress makes Your Highness look dazzling.

00:12:24.679 --> 00:12:27.080
Even the embroidery threads exude opulence.

00:12:34.279 --> 00:12:35.960
Sister, you hold only the rank of Consort.

00:12:36.080 --> 00:12:38.720
Yet you wear the Bureau of Imperial Attire's finest fabric.

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.399
Aren't you afraid it will shorten your fortune?

00:12:40.399 --> 00:12:42.120
Sister Cao, you may not know.

00:12:42.399 --> 00:12:43.480
This tender-leaf yellow is originally

00:12:43.480 --> 00:12:45.399
the first touch of yellow on the branches in spring.

00:12:45.399 --> 00:12:46.600
It best complements vitality.

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:49.320
At your current age, Sister,

00:12:52.600 --> 00:12:54.120
naturally, you cannot appreciate it.

00:12:57.679 --> 00:12:58.679
Noble Consort.

00:12:58.840 --> 00:13:00.200
Noble Concubine De felt unwell this morning

00:13:00.200 --> 00:13:01.200
and specifically asked for leave.

00:13:03.159 --> 00:13:05.480
Concubine Cao and Consort Su have arrived.

00:13:08.440 --> 00:13:10.960
Wishing Noble Consort peace and prosperity.

00:13:15.600 --> 00:13:17.639
Sister Su, you look quite radiant.

00:13:18.200 --> 00:13:20.679
This palace dress highlights your exceptional elegance.

00:13:21.519 --> 00:13:22.840
I thought that since the Noble Consort

00:13:22.840 --> 00:13:24.279
has been in low spirits these past few days,

00:13:24.279 --> 00:13:25.519
I specifically wore this dress

00:13:25.519 --> 00:13:26.759
to cheer Your Highness up.

00:13:27.159 --> 00:13:29.320
Sister Su's intentions are certainly unique.

00:13:30.120 --> 00:13:32.120
Did you forget the Empress Dowager's posthumous birthday?

00:13:34.159 --> 00:13:34.919
Sister,

00:13:35.080 --> 00:13:37.360
are you trying to cheer up the Noble Consort?

00:13:37.559 --> 00:13:38.840
I think you clearly intend

00:13:38.840 --> 00:13:40.759
to cheer up Noble Consort Meng.

00:13:40.960 --> 00:13:43.759
Sister, you wait on Noble Consort Meng hand and foot daily.

00:13:43.879 --> 00:13:45.799
You are the true expert at flattering others.

00:13:45.840 --> 00:13:47.279
I could never learn that from you.

00:13:49.639 --> 00:13:51.159
Noble Consort Meng has arrived.

00:14:05.759 --> 00:14:08.000
Consort Su and Noble Consort Meng today

00:14:08.200 --> 00:14:10.000
are truly of one mind.

00:14:11.600 --> 00:14:13.360
Consort Su has good taste.

00:14:14.039 --> 00:14:14.960
I did not intend this.

00:14:15.440 --> 00:14:16.360
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

00:14:16.879 --> 00:14:18.559
Consort Su was just saying

00:14:18.559 --> 00:14:20.399
that this tender-leaf yellow worn on her

00:14:20.399 --> 00:14:21.759
is the tender yellow of spring,

00:14:21.799 --> 00:14:23.279
but worn on others,

00:14:23.480 --> 00:14:24.879
it is the withered lotus of autumn.

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:25.879
I did not!

00:14:26.080 --> 00:14:27.120
I am wrongly accused!

00:14:27.679 --> 00:14:29.960
If I had known Your Highness favored this fabric,

00:14:30.039 --> 00:14:31.440
how would I dare compete with you in beauty?

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:34.080
Today all the consorts are dressed plainly.

00:14:34.279 --> 00:14:35.440
Only you stand out.

00:14:35.759 --> 00:14:37.559
And you claim you didn't intend to compete?

00:14:37.559 --> 00:14:38.559
Quell your anger, Your Highness.

00:14:38.840 --> 00:14:39.720
I know my mistake.

00:14:39.720 --> 00:14:40.720
I will go back and change immediately.

00:14:40.720 --> 00:14:41.399
Change?

00:14:41.799 --> 00:14:43.120
Wouldn't stripping it off be more satisfying?

00:14:43.440 --> 00:14:44.120
Someone come!

00:14:44.960 --> 00:14:45.919
Your Highness, forgive me!

00:14:46.200 --> 00:14:47.879
Your Highness, I know my mistake!

00:14:48.000 --> 00:14:49.840
Your Highness, I know my mistake!

00:14:49.840 --> 00:14:50.600
Your Highness!

00:14:51.320 --> 00:14:52.720
First, I let you fall into a predicament.

00:14:53.879 --> 00:14:55.240
Then I will find a chance to act,

00:14:55.320 --> 00:14:56.480
only then can I gain your trust.

00:15:08.399 --> 00:15:10.480
It was merely a clash of outfits.

00:15:10.960 --> 00:15:12.960
Why must Noble Consort Meng make such a fuss?

00:15:15.320 --> 00:15:16.559
Noble Consort, you may endure it,

00:15:16.759 --> 00:15:18.200
but I cannot.

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:20.320
Your generosity and tolerance

00:15:20.759 --> 00:15:22.440
only allow those with schemes in the harem

00:15:22.440 --> 00:15:23.720
to push their luck.

00:15:23.879 --> 00:15:24.679
Strip her.

00:15:24.960 --> 00:15:25.960
Noble Consort.

00:15:26.080 --> 00:15:26.879
Your Highness.

00:15:27.559 --> 00:15:28.559
I know I was wrong.

00:15:28.879 --> 00:15:30.559
I was wrong, Your Highness.

00:15:31.000 --> 00:15:31.840
Your Highness.

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:33.480
I know I was wrong.

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:34.639
Noble Consort.

00:15:34.759 --> 00:15:35.879
I was wrong.

00:15:36.039 --> 00:15:36.879
Noble Consort Meng.

00:15:38.000 --> 00:15:39.399
Today is the Empress Dowager's posthumous birthday.

00:15:39.759 --> 00:15:41.679
How can you act so recklessly?

00:15:43.279 --> 00:15:44.720
When the Empress Dowager was alive,

00:15:44.919 --> 00:15:46.480
she hated transgression the most.

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:48.559
If her spirit is watching from above,

00:15:48.759 --> 00:15:51.000
she would say I handled this correctly.

00:15:52.159 --> 00:15:54.200
To think Meng dares to contradict Wan'er like this.

00:15:57.639 --> 00:15:58.440
Today,

00:15:58.919 --> 00:16:00.840
we must not disturb her spirit's peace.

00:16:01.320 --> 00:16:03.120
Since you worry about disturbing the Empress Dowager's peace,

00:16:05.480 --> 00:16:06.279
Guards!

00:16:06.759 --> 00:16:08.519
Consort Su has offended her superiors.

00:16:08.840 --> 00:16:10.639
Drag her to the palace gates and make her kneel

00:16:10.799 --> 00:16:11.840
to enforce the palace regulations.

00:16:12.159 --> 00:16:12.960
Your Highness.

00:16:12.960 --> 00:16:13.679
The time has come.

00:16:13.679 --> 00:16:14.200
Your Highness.

00:16:15.320 --> 00:16:16.120
Your Highness.

00:16:16.799 --> 00:16:18.080
Your Highness, I know I was wrong.

00:16:18.080 --> 00:16:18.840
I know I was wrong.

00:16:18.840 --> 00:16:19.960
Your Highness, spare me!

00:16:24.279 --> 00:16:26.320
Reporting to the Noble Consort and Noble Consort Meng.

00:16:26.879 --> 00:16:28.799
Consort Su was not committing a transgression,

00:16:28.919 --> 00:16:30.200
but showing her evident filial piety.

00:16:31.039 --> 00:16:32.120
What do you mean?

00:16:32.120 --> 00:16:33.399
What sort of thing are you?

00:16:34.080 --> 00:16:35.360
Since when does a mere maid get

00:16:35.360 --> 00:16:36.840
to speak before me?

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:37.679
Slap her mouth.

00:16:41.360 --> 00:16:43.360
His Majesty arrives!